Definition: Number of siblings or spouses accompanying the passenger on board
Notes: (for example if the passenger was traveling with 2 of his/her siblings and his/her spouse, this number would be 3)

Definition: Number of parents or children accompanying the passenger on board
Notes: (for example if the passenger was traveling just with his/her mother, this number would be 1)

Definition: The ID number of the ticket

Notes: C = Cherbourg, Q = Queenstown, S = Southampton
